"What!" Quickstrike said, turning his head to see Scorponok running at him. 
He kept himself cautious, wary of what he heard. He couldn't smell anything. 
He had to rely on his sense of sight and hearing to back that up. He hadn't 
the best sense of smell on Earth. He was lucky to smell Dark Mouse's 
familiarty when Transulas had her.
